    <item>
      <title>“Keep Møving” is a piss-take on my endless to-do list. It’s about the feeling of...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DHdQYllMJjb/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/484891480_18492069982033991_248065905664729452_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzU5MzEwMDEzNjA3NTUzMjUwNzE4NDkyMDY5OTc5MDMzOTkx.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjczM3gxMzA3LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=ZZFuxa0KmbIQ7kNvwGMRdZO&amp;_nc_oc=AdoOLDWKolR4w9E3rGL4B_JsK_bnxRiY2adwmnvdsxy17mYuAniEU1NAErxUsjyXobw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=vwTDo9UO4qPXeXcm31Qopg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afz8yFmeYQQXSO3kBS219_bPfIc4aNhAbB0O-T48aKIiwQ&amp;oe=69C9905B" alt="Instagram billede fra @momomoyouth" /></p><p><strong>@momomoyouth</strong></p><p>“Keep Møving” is a piss-take on my endless to-do list. It’s about the feeling of unraveling under the weight of everybody’s expectations (including my own) while also secretly dreaming of being set free from this constantly shifting, absolutely mental Western world.<br/>
<br/>
@nicksylvester , @gloomer_ek, and Harrison Smith (@itsthedare) worked on the production, and I think it perfectly captures the urgency, the chaos, and the undeniable fun we had making it. I have never enjoyed recording ad-libs as much as I did screaming “BUAH!” in the chorus—definitely my favorite ad-libs ever. The lyrics come from a place of real frustration, but writing and performing this one heals me too.<br/>
<br/>
i hope you enjoy it!!!! shout out to @bettykrag @natscience @mikkelheriba who traveled to the cold in Norway with me to make this crazy visualizer 🪽<br/>
<br/>
Directed by @momomoyouth &amp; @bettykrag <br/>
Photography, Video &amp; Edit by @bettykrag<br/>
Visualiser produced by @mikkelheriba &amp; @sim.zar.lang.bim from @thelabcph<br/>
Makeup by @natscience<br/>
Hair Coloring by @meome_official, @michelle_meome</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/484891480_18492069982033991_248065905664729452_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzU5MzEwMDEzNjA3NTUzMjUwNzE4NDkyMDY5OTc5MDMzOTkx.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjczM3gxMzA3LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=ZZFuxa0KmbIQ7kNvwGMRdZO&amp;_nc_oc=AdoOLDWKolR4w9E3rGL4B_JsK_bnxRiY2adwmnvdsxy17mYuAniEU1NAErxUsjyXobw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=vwTDo9UO4qPXeXcm31Qopg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afz8yFmeYQQXSO3kBS219_bPfIc4aNhAbB0O-T48aKIiwQ&amp;oe=69C9905B" alt="Instagram billede fra @momomoyouth" /></p><p><strong>@momomoyouth</strong></p><p>“Keep Møving” is a piss-take on my endless to-do list. It’s about the feeling of unraveling under the weight of everybody’s expectations (including my own) while also secretly dreaming of being set free from this constantly shifting, absolutely mental Western world.<br/>
<br/>
@nicksylvester , @gloomer_ek, and Harrison Smith (@itsthedare) worked on the production, and I think it perfectly captures the urgency, the chaos, and the undeniable fun we had making it. I have never enjoyed recording ad-libs as much as I did screaming “BUAH!” in the chorus—definitely my favorite ad-libs ever. The lyrics come from a place of real frustration, but writing and performing this one heals me too.<br/>
<br/>
i hope you enjoy it!!!! shout out to @bettykrag @natscience @mikkelheriba who traveled to the cold in Norway with me to make this crazy visualizer 🪽<br/>
